<template><div><h1 id="我们需要朋友" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#我们需要朋友" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 我们需要朋友</h1>
<h3 id="we-need-friends" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#we-need-friends" aria-hidden="true">#</a> We Need Friends</h3>
<h2 id="翻译" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#翻译" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 翻译</h2>
<h4 id="the-word-friend-covers-a-wide-range-of-meanings" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#the-word-friend-covers-a-wide-range-of-meanings" aria-hidden="true">#</a> The word, friend, covers a wide range of meanings.</h4>
<p>朋友这个词的含义很广。</p>
<h4 id="it-can-be-a-nodding-acquaintance-a-comrade-a-confidant-a-partner-a-playmate-an-intimate-colleague-etc" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#it-can-be-a-nodding-acquaintance-a-comrade-a-confidant-a-partner-a-playmate-an-intimate-colleague-etc" aria-hidden="true">#</a> It can be a nodding acquaintance, a <code v-pre>comrade</code>, a confidant, a partner, a playmate, an <code v-pre>intimate</code> colleague, etc.</h4>
<p>可以是点头之交，可以是同志、可以是知己、可以是伙伴、可以是玩伴、可以是亲密的同事，等等。</p>
