<p>因为生活充满了冲突和矛盾，我们需要朋友的支持帮助我们走出困境。</p>
<h4 id="our-friends-give-us-warnings-against-danger-our-friends-offer-advice-with-regard-to-how-to-deal-with-various-situations-true-friends-share-not-only-your-joys-but-also-our-sorrows" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#our-friends-give-us-warnings-against-danger-our-friends-offer-advice-with-regard-to-how-to-deal-with-various-situations-true-friends-share-not-only-your-joys-but-also-our-sorrows" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Our friends give us warnings against danger. Our friends offer advice with regard to how to deal with various situations. True friends share not only your joys but also our sorrows.</h4>
